snippet.title: Peacemaker INDEX Award Trailer
snippet.description: A 2 minute version edited for INDEX 2009 (http://www.indexaward.dk/) based on the original Carnegie Mellon video and additional media clips from around the world (eg ABC, Al-Jazeera, Israeli Channel 2)
